能离开大教堂......","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":79},{"type":"subtitle","text":"......","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":80},{"type":"subtitle","text":"......即使会被公证所开除，我也要试一试。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":81},{"type":"subtitle","text":"带塞茜莉亚去安魂教堂。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":82},{"type":"subtitle","text":"至少让她说声再见。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":83},{"type":"subtitle","id":84},{"type":"dialog","id":85},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":86},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":87},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":88},{"type":"character","id":89},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c5/Avg_bg_26_g11_laterano_alley.png","screenadapt":"showall","id":90},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":91},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$exciting_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_exciting02_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":92,"musicid":2},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":93},{"type":"delay","time":"2","text":"","id":94},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#2$1","id":95},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"你们跑不掉的。","id":96,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e7/Avg_avg_300_phenxi_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_362_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_364_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":97},{"type":"dialogue","name":"愉快的小贩","text":"她追得好快......","id":98,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/fc/Avg_avg_npc_364_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_362_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_364_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":99},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安静的小贩","text":"怎么办怎么办，根本甩不掉......","id":100,"figure":"https://media.prts.wik