type":"dialogue","name":"愉快的小贩","text":"事情因我而起......这个黎博利不可能放过我们的，你们走！我来殿后！","id":130,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/fc/Avg_avg_npc_364_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_362_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_364_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":131},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安静的小贩","text":"你......","id":132,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/22/Avg_avg_npc_362_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_362_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_364_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":133},{"type":"dialogue","name":"愉快的小贩","text":"走！","id":134,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/fc/Avg_avg_npc_364_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":135},{"type":"character","id":136},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"退后。","id":137},{"type":"dialog","id":138},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"1.7","xstrength":"20","ystrength":"40","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":139},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_originiumcast","volume":"1","id":140},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.3","block":"true","id":141},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":142},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#3$1","id":143},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"......","id":144,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f3/Avg_avg_300_phenxi_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#7$1","id":145},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"安，多，恩......","id":146,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5b/Avg_avg_300_phenxi_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"别想再逃走......","id":147,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5b/Avg_avg_300_phenxi_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#2$1","id":148},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"1","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":149},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"给我滚出来！！！！！","id":150,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e7/Avg_avg_300_phenxi_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":151},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":152},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":153},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":154},{"type":"character","id":155},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1a/Avg_bg_26_g4_laterano_cathedralliving.png","screenadapt":"showall","id":156},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":157},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$sjoyasorrow_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_sjoyasorrow_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":158,"musicid":3},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":159},{"type":"delay","time":"2","text":"","id":160},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#3$1","name2":"avg_213_mostma_1#1$2","focus":"1","id":161},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇尔丽芙","text":"我真不明白，教宗阁下为什么对那帮“迷途者”如此......放任自流。","id":162,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/39/Avg_avg_npc_361_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#5$1","name2":"avg_213_mostma_1#1$2","focus":"1","id":163},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇尔丽芙","text":"莫斯提马，你能告诉我吗，既然你们认识？","id":164,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/23/Avg_avg_npc_361_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#5$1","name2":"avg_213_mostma_1#7$2","focus":"2","id":165},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"我可不想和你谈这个话题。","id":166,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_213_mostma_1-7$2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#5$1","name2":"avg_213_mostma_1#7$2","focus":"1","id":167},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇尔丽芙","text":"就这么记仇？","id":168,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/23/Avg_avg_npc_361_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#5$1","name2":"avg_213_mostma_1#7$2","focus":"2","id":169},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"毕竟那时候我没死在那家伙手上，却差点被你杀了呢。","id":170,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_213_mostma_1-7$2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#5$1","name2":"avg_213_mostma_1#2$2","focus":"2","id":171},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"很难忘的经历。","id":172,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ec/Avg_avg_213_mostma_1-2$2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#6$1","name2":"avg_213_mostma_1#2$2","focus":"1","id":173},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇尔丽芙","text":"这就是你在我面前一直戴着帽子的原因？不难受吗？","id":174,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/92/Avg_avg_npc_361_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#6$1","name2":"avg_213_mostma_1#7$2","focus":"2","id":175},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"都做了这么久万国信使了。戴帽子而已。","id":176,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_213_mostma_1-7$2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#6$1","name2":"avg_213_mostma_1#5$2","focus":"2","id":177},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"和你，多一事不如少一事。","id":178,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e9/Avg_avg_213_mostma_1-5$2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#5$1","name2":"avg_213_mostma_1#5$2","focus":"1","id":179},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇尔丽芙","text":"你在埋怨我吗，莫斯提马？","id":180,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/23/Avg_avg_npc_361_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#5$1","name2":"avg_213_mostma_1#2$2","focus":"2","id":181},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"拉特兰始终有拉特兰要维护的东西，也总有人要在乎这些事。我无所谓。","id":182,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ec/Avg_avg_213_mostma_1-2$2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#6$1","name2":"avg_213_mostma_1#2$2","focus":"1","id":183},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇尔丽芙","text":"莫斯提马，你可能稍微有些误解。很少有堕天使留在教廷，并不是因为教廷如何，而是因为那些堕天的萨科塔本身。","id":184,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/92/Avg_avg_npc_361_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#5$1","name2":"avg_213_mostma_1#2$2","focus":"1","id":185},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇尔丽芙","text":"我的态度也许是有一点特别......莫斯提马，你以为自己就不是个怪胎吗？","id":186,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/23/Avg_avg_npc_361_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#5$1","name2":"avg_213_mostma_1#5$2","focus":"2","id":187},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"你这么和我说话，就不怕我变成你口中那种“正常的堕天使”？","id":188,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e9/Avg_avg_213_mostma_1-5$2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#5$1","name2":"avg_213_mostma_1#5$2","focus":"1","id":189},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇尔丽芙","text":"如果你会，就听不到我和你“这么说话”了。","id":190,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/23/Avg_avg_npc_361_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#5$1","name2":"avg_213_mostma_1#8$2","focus":"2","id":191},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"行吧。说点实在的，什么时候把菲亚梅塔调走？","id":192,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/87/Avg_avg_213_mostma_1-8$2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#5$1","name2":"avg_213_mostma_1#9$2","focus":"2","id":193},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"总是跟着我，对她没好处。","id":194,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c1/Avg_avg_213_mostma_1-9$2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#6$1","name2":"avg_213_mostma_1#9$2","focus":"1","id":195},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇尔丽芙","text":"这句话你不和她本人说吗？","id":196,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/92/Avg_avg_npc_361_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#6$1","name2":"avg_213_mostma_1#10$2","focus":"2","id":197},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"说过了，没用。","id":198,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_avg_213_mostma_1-10$2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#6$1","name2":"avg_213_mostma_1#10$2","focus":"1","id":199},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇尔丽芙","text":"我说就有用吗？","id":200,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/92/Avg_avg_npc_361_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#6$1","name2":"avg_213_mostma_1#7$2","focus":"2","id":201},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"根据我的观察，权力的方便之处就是可以无视他人的意愿。","id":202,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_213_mostma_1-7$2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#1$1","name2":"avg_213_mostma_1#7$2","focus":"1","id":203},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇尔丽芙","text":"无视他人的意愿是要付出代价的......你为什么想调走菲亚梅塔，说来听听。","id":204,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d7/Avg_avg_npc_361_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#1$1","name2":"avg_213_mostma_1#7$2","focus":"2","id":205},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"菲亚梅塔说是我的护卫，你们就不好奇我有什么需要她护卫的？","id":206,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_213_mostma_1-7$2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#1$1","name2":"avg_213_mostma_1#7$2","focus":"2","id":207},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"当然，也有人觉得她是我这个堕天使的监视者。","id":208,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_213_mostma_1-7$2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#1$1","name2":"avg_213_mostma_1#2$2","focus":"2","id":209},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"这么想的人恐怕对菲亚梅塔没有丝毫了解。","id":210,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ec/Avg_avg_213_mostma_1-2$2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#1$1","name2":"avg_213_mostma_1#7$2","focus":"2","id":211},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"我不过是菲亚梅塔的饵，用来钓安多恩的。","id":212,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_213_mostma_1-7$2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#6$1","name2":"avg_213_mostma_1#7$2","focus":"1","id":213},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇尔丽芙","text":"她要是听见你这么说，恐怕不会很开心。","id":214,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/92/Avg_avg_npc_361_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#6$1","name2":"avg_213_mostma_1#5$2","focus":"2","id":215},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"好吧，那我换个说法......饵是我背上这对锁与匙。","id":216,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e9/Avg_avg_213_mostma_1-5$2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#5$1","name2":"avg_213_mostma_1#5$2","focus":"1","id":217},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇尔丽芙","text":"所以？让菲亚梅塔遂愿有什么不好吗？如果她能干掉安多恩，或者把他缉拿回大教堂，我当然乐见其成。","id":218,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/23/Avg_avg_npc_361_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#6$1","name2":"avg_213_mostma_1#5$2","focus":"1","id":219},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇尔丽芙","text":"还是说，你们俩加一块也捉不到安多恩？","id":220,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/92/Avg_avg_npc_361_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#6$1","name2":"avg_213_mostma_1#7$2","focus":"2","id":221},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"那倒不至于。只要安多恩还惦记着锁与匙，他就逃不掉。","id":222,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_213_mostma_1-7$2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#6$1","name2":"avg_213_mostma_1#1$2","focus":"2","id":223},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"只不过......我在想啊。","id":224,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/77/Avg_avg_213_mostma_1-1$2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#6$1","name2":"avg_213_mostma_1#9$2","focus":"2","id":225},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"如果安多恩已经找到别的路了呢？","id":226,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c1/Avg_avg_213_mostma_1-9$2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#6$1","name2":"avg_213_mostma_1#6$2","focus":"2","id":227},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"我不想见到的是，我走出来了，蕾缪安走出来了，甚至安多恩都走出来了......菲亚梅塔却还陷在八年前那个雨夜里。","id":228,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1a/Avg_avg_213_mostma_1-6$2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"没法和菲亚梅塔说这些。","id":229,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1a/Avg_avg_213_mostma_1-6$2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"也就是这种时候，我会稍微怀念一下共感的好处......","id":230,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1a/Avg_avg_213_mostma_1-6$2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#6$1","name2":"avg_213_mostma_1#1$2","focus":"2","id":231},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"啊，忘了菲亚梅塔是黎博利。那当我没说。","id":232,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/77/Avg_avg_213_mostma_1-1$2.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":233},{"type":"character","id":234},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":235},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_356_1#10$1","fadetime":"1.5","id":236},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":237},{"type":"dialogue","name":"教宗","text":"真是年轻的话题。","id":238,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3a/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_213_mostma_1#7$2","id":239},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"怎么，您要给我一点“过来人的教诲”吗？","id":240,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_213_mostma_1-7$2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_356_1#9$1","id":241},{"type":"dialogue","name":"教宗","text":"如果你允许我享受一下这种属于长辈的小小特权。","id":242,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b5/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_213_mostma_1#5$2","id":243},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"您请。","id":244,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e9/Avg_avg_213_mostma_1-5$2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_356_1#1$1","id":245},{"type":"dialogue","name":"教宗","text":"还记得八年前你对我说的话吗？","id":246,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/8a/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_213_mostma_1#2$2","id":247},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"......虽然我很不想破坏这么温情脉脉的气氛......","id":248,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ec/Avg_avg_213_mostma_1-2$2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_213_mostma_1#9$2","id":249},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"抱歉，阁下，真忘了。","id":250,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c1/Avg_avg_213_mostma_1-9$2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#3$1","name2":"avg_213_mostma_1#9$2","focus":"1","id":251},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇尔丽芙","text":"你说的是，“不......我还有要做的事，要保护的人”。","id":252,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/39/Avg_avg_npc_361_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#3$1","name2":"avg_213_mostma_1#11$2","focus":"2","id":253},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"......听薇尔丽芙学我说话也太恶寒了。","id":254,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d6/Avg_avg_213_mostma_1-11$2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#5$1","name2":"avg_213_mostma_1#11$2","focus":"1","id":255},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇尔丽芙","text":"......","id":256,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/23/Avg_avg_npc_361_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_356_1#6$1","id":257},{"type":"dialogue","name":"教宗","text":"彼时彼刻，你不愿让我替你做选择，此时此刻，你又何必要替菲亚梅塔做选择呢？","id":258,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b3/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_356_1#1$1","id":259},{"type":"dialogue","name":"教宗","text":"人的路总要自己去找，自己去选，自己去走。","id":260,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/8a/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"教宗","text":"薇尔，这也是给你的回答。","id":261,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/8a/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":262},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":263},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":264},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":265},{"type":"character","id":266},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/94/Avg_bg_26_g5_laterano_chapelout.png","screenadapt":"showall","id":267},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":268},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$drift_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_drift_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":269,"musicid":4},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":270},{"type":"delay","time":"2","text":"","id":271},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#9$1","focus":"1","id":272},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"......快到了，塞茜莉亚。","id":273,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f0/Avg_avg_4036_forcer_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#9$1","focus":"2","id":274},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"对不起，艾泽尔哥哥，我走得太慢了......太阳都快要落山了。","id":275,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/94/Avg_avg_npc_352_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#9$1","focus":"1","id":276},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"塞茜莉亚很了不起！毕竟没办法用公共交通......我们都走到移动地块以外啦。要是我有菲亚梅塔小姐的身手和力气，你也不用这么辛苦。","id":277,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e6/Avg_avg_4036_forcer_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#10$1","focus":"2","id":278},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"没关系的！其实妈妈也带我出来过，我们会走到离家很远的地方......和这里也差不多。","id":279,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f6/Avg_avg_npc_352_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#12$1","focus":"2","id":280},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"不过，菲亚梅塔姐姐不会发现我们偷偷来这里吗？","id":281,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ac/Avg_avg_npc_352_1-12$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#7$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#12$1","focus":"1","id":282},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"如果她只是查看终端的定位信号......希望我的花招至少能争取一点时间。","id":283,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/18/Avg_avg_4036_forcer_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"好在还是抵达了。","id":284,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/18/Avg_avg_4036_forcer_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#7$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#12$1","focus":"2","id":285},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"妈妈就是来了这里吗？","id":286,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ac/Avg_avg_npc_352_1-12$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#5$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#12$1","focus":"1","id":287},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"......塞茜莉亚，我想了很久应该怎么和你解释这件事。","id":288,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/27/Avg_avg_4036_forcer_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"费莉亚......你的妈妈，确实来了这里，但她也不在这里。","id":289,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/27/Avg_avg_4036_forcer_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"我没办法让你再见到妈妈。但在这里，你至少可以和她告别。","id":290,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/27/Avg_avg_4036_forcer_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#5$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#9$1","focus":"2","id":291},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"艾泽尔哥哥......你说的......我不太明白......","id":292,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/94/Avg_avg_npc_352_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#5$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#12$1","focus":"2","id":293},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"如果妈妈来了这里，又不在这里，那她是......又去了别的地方吗？","id":294,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ac/Avg_avg_npc_352_1-12$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"去了哪里呢？","id":295,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ac/Avg_avg_npc_352_1-12$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#12$1","focus":"1","id":296},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"......我们先进去吧。","id":297,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f0/Avg_avg_4036_forcer_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":298},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":299},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":300},{"type":"character","id":301},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f4/Avg_bg_26_g6_laterano_chapelin.png","screenadapt":"showall","id":302},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":303},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":304},{"type":"delay","time":"2","text":"","id":305},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_368_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_369_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":306},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉特兰市民","text":"......父亲去世之前，一直希望他的葬礼上只有欢笑，不要有泪水，可我却......","id":307,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6f/Avg_avg_npc_368_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_368_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_369_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":308},{"type":"dialogue","name":"温和的修士","text":"我想，令尊真正希望的是，您不因他的离去陷入无法自拔的悲伤。","id":309,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_369_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"温和的修士","text":"哭泣也好，欢笑也好，如果那就是您的道别......想必他都会欣然接受的。","id":310,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_369_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_368_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_369_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":311},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉特兰市民","text":"谢谢你......修士小姐......","id":312,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6f/Avg_avg_npc_368_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_368_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_369_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":313},{"type":"dialogue","name":"温和的修士","text":"我陪您去外面的花田走走吧。","id":314,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_369_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":315},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":316},{"type":"character","fadetime":"1.5","id":317},{"type":"delay","time":"2","text":"","id":318},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#9$1","focus":"2","id":319},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"艾泽尔哥哥，那个姐姐说她的父亲也“去世”了......","id":320,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/94/Avg_avg_npc_352_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#9$1","focus":"1","id":321},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"嗯......去世的人，就会来到这里。","id":322,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f0/Avg_avg_4036_forcer_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"活着的人，在这里与他们道别......然后，带着对去世之人的思念，继续自己的生活。","id":323,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f0/Avg_avg_4036_forcer_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#12$1","focus":"2","id":324},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"那去世的人呢，他们做什么？","id":325,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ac/Avg_avg_npc_352_1-12$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#7$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#12$1","focus":"1","id":326},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"......也许会在天上看着我们吧。","id":327,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/18/Avg_avg_4036_forcer_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#7$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#9$1","focus":"2","id":328},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"因为去了天上，所以再也见不到了吗？","id":329,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/94/Avg_avg_npc_352_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#5$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#9$1","focus":"1","id":330},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"......","id":331,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/27/Avg_avg_4036_forcer_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#9$1","focus":"1","id":332},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"塞茜莉亚，给你。","id":333,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f0/Avg_avg_4036_forcer_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#5$1","focus":"2","id":334},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"这是......妈妈的守护铳？","id":335,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c5/Avg_avg_npc_352_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#5$1","focus":"1","id":336},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"嗯。","id":337,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f0/Avg_avg_4036_forcer_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"我的爸爸妈妈，都是公证所的执行者。小时候我很少能见到他们......是爷爷把我带大的。","id":338,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f0/Avg_avg_4036_forcer_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#5$1","focus":"1","id":339},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"爷爷很喜欢他的铳，每次擦铳的时候，都会和我讲起他年轻时的事......","id":340,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e6/Avg_avg_4036_forcer_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"他参加过的战役，他的战友，他怎么遇到奶奶，还有我爸爸小时候的糗事......","id":341,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e6/Avg_avg_4036_forcer_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"看到爷爷的铳，我就会想起他讲的那些故事。","id":342,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e6/Avg_avg_4036_forcer_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#5$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#5$1","focus":"1","id":343},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"......后来，爷爷去世了。我那时也只比你现在大一点点。","id":344,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/27/Avg_avg_4036_forcer_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"公证所的执行者，带走了他的守护铳。","id":345,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/27/Avg_avg_4036_forcer_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"就像你母亲的守护铳，本应被我带走。","id":346,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/27/Avg_avg_4036_forcer_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":347},{"type":"dialog","id":348},{"type":"character","id":349},{"type":"delay","time":"3","id":350},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$distressed_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_distressed_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":351,"musicid":5},{"type":"text","text":"艾泽尔缓缓蹲下，将费莉亚的铳放在塞茜莉亚手中。","id":352},{"type":"text","text":"塞茜莉亚低下头，看着手中母亲的守护铳。","id":353},{"type":"text","text":"艾泽尔轻轻握住塞茜莉亚的手。","id":354},{"type":"text","text":"温热的水滴跌落在守护铳的浮雕花纹上，流到年幼女孩的掌心，堆积成一小片水渍。","id":355},{"type":"dialog","id":356},{"type":"delay","time":"0.51","id":357},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#5$1","focus":"2","id":358},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"艾泽尔哥哥......我怎么哭了......","id":359,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c5/Avg_avg_npc_352_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#7$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#5$1","focus":"1","id":360},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"我按爷爷教我的，每周给后院的盆栽浇水，后来它们开花了，我很高兴，喊爷爷来看。","id":361,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/18/Avg_avg_4036_forcer_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#5$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#5$1","focus":"1","id":362},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"喊出声才想起来，爷爷已经不在了。","id":363,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/27/Avg_avg_4036_forcer_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"我再也见不到爷爷，再也没见过他的铳。","id":364,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/27/Avg_avg_4036_forcer_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"死亡就是永不再会的离别。","id":365,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/27/Avg_avg_4036_forcer_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_352_1#7$1","id":366},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"......","id":367,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/09/Avg_avg_npc_352_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":368},{"type":"character","id":369},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":370},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_351_1#1$1","blackstart":"0.2","blackend":"0.7","fadetime":"2","id":371},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":372},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"然而离别本身即是对死亡的克服。","id":373,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e6/Avg_avg_npc_351_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"存者在此，去者在彼，才有“离别”。","id":374,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e6/Avg_avg_npc_351_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"“离别”是生者对逝者的惦念，也因此成为逝者存在的证明。","id":375,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e6/Avg_avg_npc_351_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":376},{"type":"character","id":377},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":378},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_351_1#1$1","fadetime":"1","id":379},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":380},{"type":"dialogue","name":"修士","text":"这就是为何我们需要道别。","id":381,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e6/Avg_avg_npc_351_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":382},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":383},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":384},{"type":"dialog","id":385},{"type":"character","id":386},{"type":"image","id":387}],"characters":["艾泽尔","菲亚梅塔","愉快的小贩","安静的小贩","塞茜莉亚","？？？","薇尔丽芙","莫斯提马","教宗","拉特兰市民","温和的修士","修士"]}